<style>
body {
    height: 100vh;
    display: block;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
}

.failed-container {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    background-color: #ffffff;
}

.cross-icon {
    color: #dc3545;
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}
</style>
<body>

<div class="container failed-container animate__animated animate__fadeIn p-5 mt-5">
    <div class="cross-icon">&#10006;</div>
    <h2 class="mb-4">Thanh toán thất bại</h2>
    <p>Xin lỗi vì sự bất tiện này. Vui lòng thử lại hoặc liên hệ hỗ trợ.</p>
    <form>
        <!-- Include any additional form elements or customization as needed -->
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger">Quay lại trang chủ</button>
    </form>
</div>

<script src="https://unpkg.com/ionicons@5.6.3/dist/ionicons.js"></script>
<script src="/js/jquery.magnific-popup.min.js"></script>
<script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/4.1.1/animate.min.js"></script>

<script>
    // Example: Initialize Magnific Popup for a button
    $(document).ready(function() {
        $('.btn-danger').magnificPopup({
            type: 'block',
            preloader: false,
            focus: '#username',
            modal: true
        });
    });
</script>